org.apache.ambari.server.audit.request.eventcreator

Interface RequestAuditEventCreator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AlertGroupEventCreator, AlertTargetEventCreator, BlueprintEventCreator, BlueprintExportEventCreator, ComponentEventCreator, ConfigurationChangeEventCreator, CredentialEventCreator, DefaultEventCreator, GroupEventCreator, HostEventCreator, MemberEventCreator, PrivilegeEventCreator, RecommendationIgnoreEventCreator, RepositoryEventCreator, RepositoryVersionEventCreator, RequestEventCreator, ServiceConfigDownloadEventCreator, ServiceEventCreator, UnauthorizedEventCreator, UpgradeEventCreator, UpgradeItemEventCreator, UserEventCreator, ValidationIgnoreEventCreator, ViewInstanceEventCreator, ViewPrivilegeEventCreator

    public interface RequestAuditEventCreator
    This interface must be implemented by the plugins for the request audit logger in order to make custom AuditEvents based on Request.Types and Resource.Type
